{
  "video_id": "RD_SLJG7oi8",
  "title": "Why design should include everyone | Sin√©ad Burke",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12613.0,
      "end_time": 14860.0,
      "text": "I want to give you a new perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15820.0,
      "end_time": 18660.0,
      "text": "That sounds grandiose, and it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19380.0,
      "end_time": 21990.0,
      "text": "I left Ireland yesterday morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21700.0,
      "end_time": 24156.0,
      "text": "I traveled from Dublin to New York"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24180.0,
      "end_time": 25380.0,
      "text": "independently."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25900.0,
      "end_time": 27796.0,
      "text": "But the design of an airport,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27820.0,
      "end_time": 30356.0,
      "text": "plane and terminal"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30380.0,
      "end_time": 34300.0,
      "text": "offers little independence when you&#39;re 105 and a half centimeters tall."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35200.0,
      "end_time": 38260.0,
      "text": "For Americans, that&#39;s 3&#39; 5\"."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39500.0,
      "end_time": 43220.0,
      "text": "I was whisked through the airport by airline assistants in a wheelchair."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43820.0,
      "end_time": 46820.0,
      "text": "Now, I don&#39;t need to use a wheelchair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47500.0,
      "end_time": 49596.0,
      "text": "but the design of an airport"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49620.0,
      "end_time": 51876.0,
      "text": "and its lack of accessibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51900.0,
      "end_time": 53980.0,
      "text": "means that it&#39;s my only way to get through."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55100.0,
      "end_time": 57836.0,
      "text": "With my carry-on bag between my feet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57860.0,
      "end_time": 61236.0,
      "text": "I was wheeled through security, preclearance"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 63620.0,
      "text": "and I arrived at my boarding gate."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64700.0,
      "end_time": 67556.0,
      "text": "I use the accessibility services in the airport"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67580.0,
      "end_time": 70820.0,
      "text": "because most of the terminal is just not designed with me in mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71740.0,
      "end_time": 73460.0,
      "text": "Take security, for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74140.0,
      "end_time": 77236.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not strong enough to lift my carry-on bag"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77260.0,
      "end_time": 79300.0,
      "text": "from the ground to the carousel."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 80300.0,
      "end_time": 81899.0,
      "text": "I stand at eye level with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82380.0,
      "end_time": 87316.0,
      "text": "And those who work in that space for safety purposes cannot help me"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 87340.0,
      "end_time": 89200.0,
      "text": "and cannot do it for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 90200.0,
      "end_time": 93780.0,
      "text": "Design inhibits my autonomy and my independence."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 94820.0,
      "end_time": 98300.0,
      "text": "But traveling at this size, it isn&#39;t all bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 98780.0,
      "end_time": 101556.0,
      "text": "The leg room in economy is like business class."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 101580.0,
      "end_time": 103460.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 104580.0,
      "end_time": 106660.0,
      "text": "I often forget that I&#39;m a little person."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 107180.0,
      "end_time": 111140.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the physical environment and society that remind me."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 111940.0,
      "end_time": 115899.0,
      "text": "Using a public bathroom is an excruciating experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 116700.0,
      "end_time": 118876.0,
      "text": "I walk into the cubicle"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 118900.0,
      "end_time": 120758.0,
      "text": "but I can&#39;t reach the lock on the door."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 121700.0,
      "end_time": 124600.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m creative and resilient."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 124820.0,
      "end_time": 128220.0,
      "text": "I look around and see if there&#39;s a bin that I can turn upside down."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 129220.0,
      "end_time": 130419.0,
      "text": "Is it safe?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 130860.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132600.0,
      "text": "Not really."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 132460.0,
      "end_time": 134780.0,
      "text": "Is it hygienic and sanitary?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 136459.0,
      "text": "Definitely not."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 137580.0,
      "end_time": 139200.0,
      "text": "But the alternative is much worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 140600.0,
      "end_time": 142600.0,
      "text": "If that doesn&#39;t work, I use my phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 142980.0,
      "end_time": 146360.0,
      "text": "It gives me an additional four- to six-inch reach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 146600.0,
      "end_time": 148740.0,
      "text": "and I try to jam the lock closed with my iPhone."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 149540.0,
      "end_time": 153956.0,
      "text": "Now, I imagine that&#39;s not what Jony Ive had in mind when he designed the iPhone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 153980.0,
      "end_time": 155179.0,
      "text": "but it works."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 156780.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "The alternative is that I approach a stranger."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 160300.0,
      "end_time": 162556.0,
      "text": "I apologize profusely"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 162580.0,
      "end_time": 165660.0,
      "text": "and I ask them to stand guard outside my cubicle door."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 166820.0,
      "end_time": 168356.0,
      "text": "They do"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 168380.0,
      "end_time": 170340.0,
      "text": "and I emerge grateful"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 171300.0,
      "end_time": 172980.0,
      "text": "but absolutely mortified,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 173860.0,
      "end_time": 175596.0,
      "text": "and hope that they didn&#39;t notice"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 175620.0,
      "end_time": 177954.0,
      "text": "that I left the bathroom without washing my hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 179200.0,
      "end_time": 182260.0,
      "text": "I carry hand sanitizer with me every single day"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 183600.0,
      "end_time": 188396.0,
      "text": "because the sink, soap dispenser, hand dryer and mirror"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 188420.0,
      "end_time": 189780.0,
      "text": "are all out of my reach."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 190940.0,
      "end_time": 193676.0,
      "text": "Now, the accessible bathroom is somewhat of an option."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 193700.0,
      "end_time": 196100.0,
      "text": "In this space, I can reach the lock on the door,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 196660.0,
      "end_time": 201200.0,
      "text": "the sink, the soap dispenser, the hand dryer and the mirror."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 202220.0,
      "end_time": 205140.0,
      "text": "Yet, I cannot use the toilet."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 206340.0,
      "end_time": 208796.0,
      "text": "It is deliberately designed higher"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 208820.0,
      "end_time": 211980.0,
      "text": "so that wheelchair users can transfer across with ease."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 213200.0,
      "end_time": 216380.0,
      "text": "This is a wonderful and necessary innovation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 217260.0,
      "end_time": 221500.0,
      "text": "but in the design world, when we describe a new project or idea as accessible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 222500.0,
      "end_time": 223700.0,
      "text": "what does that mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 224740.0,
      "end_time": 226660.0,
      "text": "Who is it accessible to?"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 227660.0,
      "end_time": 230420.0,
      "text": "And whose needs are not being accommodated for?"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 231820.0,
      "end_time": 233316.0,
      "text": "Now, the bathroom is an example"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 233340.0,
      "end_time": 235860.0,
      "text": "of where design impinges upon my dignity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 236740.0,
      "end_time": 240260.0,
      "text": "but the physical environment impacts upon me in much more casual ways too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 241600.0,
      "end_time": 243300.0,
      "text": "something as simple as ordering a cup of coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 244140.0,
      "end_time": 245500.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;ll admit it."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 245980.0,
      "end_time": 247859.0,
      "text": "I drink far too much coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 248300.0,
      "end_time": 250876.0,
      "text": "My order is a skinny vanilla latte,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 250900.0,
      "end_time": 253460.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;m trying to wean myself off the syrup."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 254620.0,
      "end_time": 257356.0,
      "text": "But the coffee shop, it&#39;s not designed well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 257380.0,
      "end_time": 258579.0,
      "text": "at least not for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 259339.0,
      "end_time": 262116.0,
      "text": "Queuing, I&#39;m standing beside the pastry cabinet"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 262140.0,
      "end_time": 264180.0,
      "text": "and the barista calls for the next order."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 265200.0,
      "end_time": 267219.0,
      "text": "\"Next, please!\" they shout."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 268260.0,
      "end_time": 269460.0,
      "text": "They can&#39;t see me."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 270460.0,
      "end_time": 273275.0,
      "text": "The person next to me in the queue points to my existence"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 273300.0,
      "end_time": 275540.0,
      "text": "and everyone is embarrassed."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 276600.0,
      "end_time": 279340.0,
      "text": "I order as quick as I can and I move along to collect my coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 280300.0,
      "end_time": 282740.0,
      "text": "Now, think just for a second."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 283380.0,
      "end_time": 284580.0,
      "text": "Where do they put it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 285780.0,
      "end_time": 287619.0,
      "text": "Up high and without a lid."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 288300.0,
      "end_time": 291196.0,
      "text": "Reaching up to collect a coffee that I have paid for"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 291220.0,
      "end_time": 293660.0,
      "text": "is an incredibly dangerous experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 294460.0,
      "end_time": 297715.0,
      "text": "But design also impinges on the clothes that I want to wear."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 297740.0,
      "end_time": 300380.0,
      "text": "I want garments that reflect my personality."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 301140.0,
      "end_time": 303820.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s difficult to find in the childrenswear department."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 304460.0,
      "end_time": 307739.0,
      "text": "And often womenswear requires far too many alterations."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 308420.0,
      "end_time": 313140.0,
      "text": "I want shoes that affect my maturity, professionalism and sophistication."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 313980.0,
      "end_time": 318220.0,
      "text": "Instead, I&#39;m offered sneakers with Velcro straps and light-up shoes."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 319200.0,
      "end_time": 322796.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;m not totally opposed to light-up shoes."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 322820.0,
      "end_time": 324200.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 324900.0,
      "end_time": 328316.0,
      "text": "But design also impacts on such simple things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 328340.0,
      "end_time": 329780.0,
      "text": "like sitting on a chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 330740.0,
      "end_time": 334260.0,
      "text": "I cannot go from a standing to a seating position with grace."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 335140.0,
      "end_time": 338395.0,
      "text": "Due to the standards of design heights of chairs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 338420.0,
      "end_time": 341116.0,
      "text": "I have to crawl on my hands and knees"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 341140.0,
      "end_time": 342756.0,
      "text": "just to get on top of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 342780.0,
      "end_time": 346419.0,
      "text": "whilst also being conscious that it might tip over at any stage."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 347940.0,
      "end_time": 349756.0,
      "text": "But whilst design impacts on me"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 349780.0,
      "end_time": 354556.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s a chair, a bathroom, a coffee shop, or clothes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 354580.0,
      "end_time": 357756.0,
      "text": "I rely on and benefit"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 357780.0,
      "end_time": 359580.0,
      "text": "from the kindness of strangers."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 361340.0,
      "end_time": 362979.0,
      "text": "But not everybody is so nice."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 364220.0,
      "end_time": 366796.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m reminded that I&#39;m a little person"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 366820.0,
      "end_time": 368260.0,
      "text": "when a stranger points,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 369340.0,
      "end_time": 370539.0,
      "text": "stares,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 371140.0,
      "end_time": 372340.0,
      "text": "laughs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 373180.0,
      "end_time": 374956.0,
      "text": "calls me a name,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 374980.0,
      "end_time": 376460.0,
      "text": "or takes a photograph of me."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 377780.0,
      "end_time": 379208.0,
      "text": "This happens almost every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 380540.0,
      "end_time": 383436.0,
      "text": "With the rise of social media, it has given me an opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 383460.0,
      "end_time": 387419.0,
      "text": "and a platform to have a voice as a blogger and as an activist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 388260.0,
      "end_time": 390556.0,
      "text": "but it has also made me nervous"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 390580.0,
      "end_time": 392676.0,
      "text": "that I might become a meme"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 392700.0,
      "end_time": 394260.0,
      "text": "or a viral sensation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 395220.0,
      "end_time": 396620.0,
      "text": "all without my consent."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 398600.0,
      "end_time": 400756.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s take a moment right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 400780.0,
      "end_time": 402380.0,
      "text": "to make something very clear."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 403540.0,
      "end_time": 405940.0,
      "text": "The word \"midget\" is a slur."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 407180.0,
      "end_time": 411300.0,
      "text": "It evolved from PT Barnum&#39;s era of circuses and freak shows."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 412460.0,
      "end_time": 414180.0,
      "text": "Society has evolved."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 415340.0,
      "end_time": 416859.0,
      "text": "So should our vocabulary."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 417660.0,
      "end_time": 420360.0,
      "text": "Language is a powerful tool."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 420600.0,
      "end_time": 422600.0,
      "text": "It does not just name our society."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 422540.0,
      "end_time": 423980.0,
      "text": "It shapes it."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 424700.0,
      "end_time": 428116.0,
      "text": "I am incredibly proud to be a little person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 428140.0,
      "end_time": 431395.0,
      "text": "to have inherited the condition of achondroplasia."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 431420.0,
      "end_time": 433660.0,
      "text": "But I am most proud to be Sinead."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 434500.0,
      "end_time": 437540.0,
      "text": "Achondroplasia is the most common form of dwarfism."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 438220.0,
      "end_time": 441780.0,
      "text": "Achondroplasia translates as \"without cartilage formation.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 442580.0,
      "end_time": 446316.0,
      "text": "I have short limbs and achondroplastic facial features,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 446340.0,
      "end_time": 448659.0,
      "text": "my forehead and my nose."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 449380.0,
      "end_time": 451996.0,
      "text": "My arms do not straighten fully,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 452200.0,
      "end_time": 453900.0,
      "text": "but I can lick my elbow."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 454460.0,
      "end_time": 455840.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not showing you that one."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 457200.0,
      "end_time": 461500.0,
      "text": "Achondroplasia occurs in approximately one in every 20,000 births."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 462340.0,
      "end_time": 466200.0,
      "text": "80 percent of little people are born to two average-height parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 466820.0,
      "end_time": 470740.0,
      "text": "That means that anybody in this room could have a child with achondroplasia."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 471780.0,
      "end_time": 475299.0,
      "text": "Yet, I inherited my condition from my dad."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 475700.0,
      "end_time": 477979.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to show you a photo of my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 479100.0,
      "end_time": 481116.0,
      "text": "My mother is average height,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 481140.0,
      "end_time": 483356.0,
      "text": "my father is a little person"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 483380.0,
      "end_time": 485380.0,
      "text": "and I am the eldest of five children."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 486200.0,
      "end_time": 488539.0,
      "text": "I have three sisters and one brother."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 489380.0,
      "end_time": 491600.0,
      "text": "They are all average height."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 491980.0,
      "end_time": 495396.0,
      "text": "I am incredibly fortunate to have been born into a family"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 495420.0,
      "end_time": 498620.0,
      "text": "that cultivated my curiosity and my tenacity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 499540.0,
      "end_time": 504516.0,
      "text": "that protected me from the unkindness and ignorance of strangers"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 504540.0,
      "end_time": 508716.0,
      "text": "and that armed me with the resilience, creativity and confidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 508740.0,
      "end_time": 513380.0,
      "text": "that I needed to survive and manipulate the physical environment and society."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 514620.0,
      "end_time": 518436.0,
      "text": "If I was to pinpoint any reason why I am successful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 518460.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522580.00000000006,
      "text": "it is because I was and I am a loved child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 523380.0,
      "end_time": 527276.0,
      "text": "now, a loved child with a lot of sass and sarcasm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 527300.0,
      "end_time": 528978.0,
      "text": "but a loved child nonetheless."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 530180.0,
      "end_time": 533140.0,
      "text": "In giving you an insight into who I am today"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 534100.0,
      "end_time": 536200.0,
      "text": "I wanted to offer you a new perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 537200.0,
      "end_time": 538476.0,
      "text": "I wanted to challenge the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 538500.0,
      "end_time": 542600.0,
      "text": "that design is but a tool to create function and beauty."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 543100.0,
      "end_time": 546100.0,
      "text": "Design greatly impacts upon people&#39;s lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 547220.0,
      "end_time": 548500.0,
      "text": "all lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 549180.0,
      "end_time": 552876.0,
      "text": "Design is a way in which we can feel included in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 552900.0,
      "end_time": 557156.0,
      "text": "but it is also a way in which we can uphold a person&#39;s dignity"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 557180.0,
      "end_time": 558540.0,
      "text": "and their human rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 559420.0,
      "end_time": 562116.0,
      "text": "Design can also inflict vulnerability"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 562140.0,
      "end_time": 564620.0,
      "text": "on a group whose needs aren&#39;t considered."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 566140.0,
      "end_time": 569980.0,
      "text": "So today, I want your perceptions challenged."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 570700.0,
      "end_time": 572796.0,
      "text": "Who are we not designing for?"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 572820.0,
      "end_time": 575636.0,
      "text": "How can we amplify their voices"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 575660.0,
      "end_time": 577260.0,
      "text": "and their experiences?"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 578200.0,
      "end_time": 579220.0,
      "text": "What is the next step?"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 580220.0,
      "end_time": 582796.0,
      "text": "Design is an enormous privilege,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 582820.0,
      "end_time": 584780.0,
      "text": "but it is a bigger responsibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 585780.0,
      "end_time": 587819.0,
      "text": "I want you to open your eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 588580.0,
      "end_time": 589796.0,
      "text": "Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 589820.0,
      "end_time": 593580.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}